Please follw this Video foe Jenkins Integration with Email
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CXdfVJxK1OQ

Please Follow this Steps:-

For this we need SMTP server details. using SMTP detail we send email notification as part of Jenkins Job.

Manage Jenkins=>Configure system=> E-mail Notification

SMTP Server:- smtp.gmail.com
click on Advanced
Check Use SMTP Authentication
User Name:- Put the email id.(abc@gmail.com)
Password:- password of the abc@gmail.com
Check Use SSL
SMTP Port:- 465
Test the Configuration by sending test e-mail.
Test e-mail recipient(abc@gmail.com)
